latform_icon3-1.svg alt data-no-retina></div><h3>Headcount Planning</h3><p><p>Model, forecast, and execute on different growth scenarios with a highly visual and collaborative process so you can deliver headcount planning without the headache.</p></p> <a href=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/platform/headcount-planning/ class=readmore>Learn more</a></div></div><div class=item><div class=platform_image_place style="background: url(https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/wp-content/themes/charthop/img/platform1.svg) no-repeat; background-size: cover;"><div> <img src=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Manager-tools_header.png alt></div></div><div class=platform_box><div class=platform_icon> <img src=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Illo_ManagerTools.svg alt data-no-retina></div><h3>Manager Tools</h3><p><p>Help everyone pull in the same direction by giving your managers everything they need to monitor performance and progression through 1:1s and access to people profiles, compensation, and performance data.</p></p> <a href=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/platform/manager-tools/ class=readmore>Learn more</a></div></div><div class=item><div class=platform_image_place style="background: url(https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/wp-content/themes/charthop/img/platform1.svg) no-repeat; background-size: cover;"><div> <img src=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Employee-tools_header.png alt></div></div><div class=platform_box><div class=platform_icon> <img src=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Illo_EmployeeTools.svg alt data-no-retina></div><h3>Employee Tools</h3><p><p>Can you name your latest hire, where she sits, and her favorite ice cream? Now you can with rich profiles that include personal interests, name pronunciations, gender pronouns, and more.</p></p> <a href=https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/platform/employee-tools/ class=readmore>Learn more</a></div></div><div class=i